channel.title: [VFX] Demon Warp
channel.description:
Still getting used to AE, im pretty comfortable with it right now but as i was learning i did a face warp of myself and my sister wanted one. Hers came out better because it was the 3rd one i did.
I dont have a very good camera so bare with me.
[url=http://vimeo.com/5160382][img]http://img199.imageshack.us/img199/8144/emwarp.png[/img][/url] http://vimeo.com/5160382
